    "title": "未来の“景色”",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "サイレンススズカのファン交流イベントが\r\n開かれているのを偶然見かけ、\n少しのぞいていくことにした。",
            "enText": "I happened to see a Silence Suzuka fan event \ngoing on, so I decided to take a look.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": 8891903649017869941
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": 7378135571957987181
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7752011104925898094,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "司会者",
            "enName": "Host",
            "jpText": "……はい、ここからはスズカさんへの\r\n質問コーナーになります！\nでは1番早かった、そこの方から！",
            "enText": "… Yes, this will be a question-and-answer \nsection for you, Suzuka! Let's start with \nthe one who was the fastest!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 5740079372515953974
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": -6609178465700642138
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8674803563001377548,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アンニュイなファン",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――スズカさんは、\r\n休日は何をして過ごされてるんですか？",
            "enText": "—What do you do on your \ndays off, Suzuka-san?",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 2191989531835776217
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": 2877179392072739966
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": -5317453169749262882
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4912747641966557286,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "はい、休日は……走ってます。",
            "enText": "Yes, I run… on my days off.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": -3879624432725186078
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 28,
                    "pathId": 3084714296724154506
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -3457366652472890912
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9136177389128725968,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "おずおず聞くファン",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――あの、スズカさんが普段気晴らしに\r\nしていることってありますか？",
            "enText": "—What do you usually do \nto distract yourself?",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": 9041893428698153666
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 166,
                    "pathId": -8265004031213175687
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 165,
                    "pathId": 3924365700700744772
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2438683132815771847,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "走ること……でしょうか。",
            "enText": "Is it… to run?",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 60,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": -3114761189973561734
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 6307622509946312277
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7722942306795622183,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "遠慮がちなファン",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――え、ええと……じゃあ、\r\nスズカさんの趣味は……。",
            "enText": "—Yes, uh… Then, Suzuka's hobby is…",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 141,
                    "pathId": 8545827436384354164
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 168,
                    "pathId": -6757966627997827142
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1500173982885176859,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "走ること……ですね。\r\n…………。",
            "enText": "Running……",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": 173293332713209607
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -4075856456238859847
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7953212954436736845,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "あ……でも。",
            "enText": "Oh, and…",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 52,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 29,
                    "pathId": -754148476099103748
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 63,
                    "pathId": -2334616650644569944
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1507810803531365531,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "遠慮がちなファン",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "おっ！？",
            "enText": "Whoa!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 50,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": 8923404211050156831
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": 4376591345609789895
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7020793466909775170,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "いちご大福は――好きですね。",
            "enText": "I like strawberry daifuku.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 8036957631755861486
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -4559948762057516261
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3289087013958578606,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "遠慮がちなファン",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――そ、そうですか……。",
            "enText": "—Yes, I see…",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 60,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -8803491611692249195
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 2799968050364976524
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8005692976339493730,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……何を聞いても回答は『走る』の連続。\r\nさすがに質問の勢いも弱くなってきていたが、\nそこへ――",
            "enText": "… No matter what I asked, the answer was \nalways \"run\". The momentum of the questions \nwas getting weaker, but then—",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 7682672518439050924
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 3053459796576630386
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3442184526809412642,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "知的な雰囲気のファン",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "で、ではその……スズカさんは……\r\nなぜ“走る”んですか？",
            "enText": "So, then, why do you… \"run\"?",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 183,
                    "pathId": -1565633896996190518
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 171,
                    "pathId": -5342511721920641225
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1556001966337270395,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "…………。\r\nなぜ……ですか。",
            "enText": "… Why…?",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 39,
                    "pathId": 6971043375102656109
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": 7828744599025168365
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1897433313922828362,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "知的な雰囲気のファン",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "はい。走り切った後、いつも……\r\n本当に、いい顔をされていますし。\nその根っこにある理由は、なんなのかな、と。",
            "enText": "Yes. After a run, you always look \nreally good on… I wonder what is \nthe root reason for that.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 116,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 127,
                    "pathId": -6366295434736354302
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 127,
                    "pathId": -7903330498801372642
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6065761963051611923,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "そうですね。……やっぱり、それは……\r\n走るのが好きだから、ですね。",
            "enText": "Yes, I do. After all, it's because… \nI like to run, isn't it?",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": 6479216978320031559
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": -3164408833899218239
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5263943695985195424,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "……1度は“勝たなきゃいけないから”\r\nそうしないといけないから走るんだ、と\n思った時期もありました。",
            "enText": "…1 There was a time when I thought \nthat I was running because I had \nto, because I had to win.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -1680513454849211482
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -472174069384153156
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7576607451602482147,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "でも、いろんな人と出会って、\r\n一緒に走って……最初の、純粋な\n気持ちを思い出すことができました。",
            "enText": "However, I met many people and ran together \nwith them, and I was able to remember the \nfirst pure feeling of…",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": 6412114753395121164
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": 4018396758140402602
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5973154492667719891,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "真面目そうなファン",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……じゃあ、走っていて、\r\n1番気持ちいい瞬間っていうのは、\nいつなんですか？",
            "enText": "… So, when do you feel the \nbest when you are running?",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 177,
                    "pathId": -7718804711931060366
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 190,
                    "pathId": 4821036948300826876
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7971637490759151020,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "それは……望んでいた“景色”が\r\n見られた時、ですね。",
            "enText": "That's when you see the \"view\" \nyou've been hoping for.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 64,
                    "pathId": -2243352639116990784
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 2310538357797106911
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3784379772102532418,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "昔から好きだったんです。誰もいない……\r\nただ地面を踏みしめる音だけが響く、\n静かな道を、思い切り走っていく――",
            "enText": "I've always liked it. There was no one to be \nseen… I ran as fast as I could along the \nquiet road where the only sound was the \ntread on the ground.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": -3123109731905534813
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": -8658244140790149863
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1281565872344028605,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "本当に、本当に……その“景色”は\r\n綺麗で――今でも、私はそれを求めて、\nレースを走っているんです。",
            "enText": "It's really, really… beautiful, and I'm \nstill running races for it.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -1690281479282106831
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 121,
                    "pathId": -3263322945695506383
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6079226753093569300,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "……それに、今は他にも\r\n嬉しいことがあります。",
            "enText": "… And there's something else that \nmakes me happy right now.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": 5374006600864266830
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": -6716771672578715623
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6547757706232806855,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "私が走ることで、周りで支えてくれる\r\nみなさんにも、見たことのないような走り……\n見たことのない“景色”を見せてあげられる。",
            "enText": "By running, I can show the people around me, \nwho support me, a \"view\" of running that \nthey have never seen before…",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 125,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 136,
                    "pathId": 4363262822882561688
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 136,
                    "pathId": 4905551543483655808
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6568251866812180571,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "それは、とても……\r\n素晴らしいことなんじゃないかって、\n思えるようになりましたから。",
            "enText": "I've come to think that it's \na very… wonderful thing.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": -1869792668353969867
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": -8851872440954493670
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2061794851236474959,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "熱いファン",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――おぉっ……！　スズカさん……！",
            "enText": "—Oh…! Suzuka…!",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 152,
                    "pathId": -2924914787779394135
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": -7140525780589669494
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1302198102139480586,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "いつの間にか、会場の空気は変わっていた。\r\n客席は沸き立ち、新たな質問が次々と飛ぶ。\n――サイレンススズカの走りへの想いに。",
            "enText": "Before I knew it, the atmosphere in the hall \nhad changed. The audience was boiling, and \nnew questions were being asked one after \nanother. —to their thoughts on Silence \nSuzuka's run.",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 125,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 136,
                    "pathId": 1283146968804836238
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 136,
                    "pathId": 4678413471875257890
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4282712388521553186,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "盛り上がるファン",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その……“景色”を見せる相手には、\r\nファンも入っているんですか！？",
            "enText": "Does that… include your fans in the \n\"scenery\" you show them?",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": -5550199222575391999
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": 1095669800595615350
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1905798235410716108,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "はい……もちろん。\r\nこれからもずっと、私は“景色”を\n求めて、走り続けます。",
            "enText": "Yes… of course. I will continue to \nrun in search of \"scenery\".",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": 5796040564720198178
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 1877532803068001295
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8886601076921573606,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "自分のため、支えてくれるみなさんのため……\r\nたくさんの人に、見たことのない“景色”を、\n見せてあげたいですから。",
            "enText": "For myself and for the people who support \nme… I want to show many people a \"view\" \nthat they have never seen before.",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 139,
                    "pathId": 6756595617107110124
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 130,
                    "pathId": -2670910903287283765
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3874988424627367168,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "サイレンススズカ",
            "enName": "Silence Suzuka",
            "jpText": "なので――どうか、これからも\r\n見守っていてください。私の……走りを――",
            "enText": "So please continue to watch over me. Please \nkeep watching my… run.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 139,
                    "pathId": -5864023967472315567
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 5722308548370907
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9124263760744211815,
            "blockIdx": 32
        }
    ],
